A quick blog post today about a question I often see on discord, facebook, &hellip;
How do I setup weapon that can be used in one hand or two hands like longswords or spears.
The main problem is the difference between stats when you use the weapon with one hand or two hands. And the system doesn&rsquo;t have any way to have different stats in the same weapon depending on how mane hands you use.
